headline: Drug Development Inputs & Services Stocks Q1 In Review: Repligen (NASDAQ:RGEN) Vs Peers
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Repligen (NASDAQ:RGEN) and the best and worst performers in the drug development inputs & services industry.
